---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Daily Student Life | Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura"
  description="See how a typical day unfolds for residents at Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura with study hours, mentoring, and wellness time built in."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Girls PG near Osmanpura</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Daily Student Life</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Jyoti Girls PG maintains a calm, motivating routine so students balancing NEET prep, college lectures, or internships can perform their best.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">A Structured Day for Focused Learners</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Morning Momentum</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Residents begin with a nutritious breakfast by 7:30 AM, followed by library hour and shuttle departures to nearby coaching classes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Afternoon Balance</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Post-lunch quiet hours, group study pods, and mentor check-ins help students consolidate their lessons before evening revisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Evening Wind-Down</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">After dinner, residents enjoy terrace walks, recreation time, and curated wellness sessions before the 10:00 PM roll call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Study Tools &amp; Accountability</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Dedicated silent floors two minutes away from Osmanpura coaching hubs.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Weekly score-tracking meetings for NEET and competitive exam aspirants.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Subject-wise notice boards highlighting upcoming tests and college submissions.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">High-speed Wi-Fi with router redundancy to prevent downtime during peak study slots.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Community &amp; Wellbeing</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Mentor Evenings</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Resident caretakers host "focus circles" every Wednesday so students can voice challenges and find solutions together.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Weekend Boosters</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Yoga, art therapy, and movie nights are scheduled on rotational weekends without disturbing study plans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Parents' Connect</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Monthly video walkthroughs keep families updated on room maintenance, attendance, and academic progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="visit">Plan a campus tour</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20can%20I%20visit%20to%20understand%20the%20daily%20routine%3F" class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chat with our team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
